# Layout (`guest/shell` + `portal/shell` + `shared/ui`)

## Structure

- `PortalShellComponent` (`portal-shell`) — grid: sidebar column + `portal-shell__main` (topbar + scrollable `router-outlet` content).
- `PortalSidebarComponent` (`portal-sidebar`) — brand row (BHCOM + portal suffix from `PORTAL_CONFIG`), collapsible nav (desktop), drawer (mobile).
- Nav types: `portal/common/models/nav.model.ts`; configs: `portal/employee/employee-nav.config.ts`, `portal/admin/admin-nav.config.ts`.
- `PORTAL_CONFIG` provided on shell route in `employee.routes.ts` / `admin.routes.ts` (sidebar injects nav + `shell.brandSuffixKey`).
- `PortalTopbarComponent` (`portal-topbar`) — hamburger (mobile only), theme/notifications/profile actions.
- `LanguagePickerComponent` (`shared/ui/language-picker/`) — globe language menu; shared by portal topbar and guest topbar.
- `ThemePickerComponent` (`shared/ui/theme-picker/`) — light/dark theme menu; shared by portal topbar and guest topbar.
- **Guest layout** (`guest/shell/`) — `GuestShellComponent` (topbar + scrollable outlet + optional footer), `GuestTopbarComponent`, `GuestFooterComponent`, `PortalCardComponent`. Used for `/`, `/sign-in`, `/login`, `/admin/login`, `/admin/register`. No sidebar.
- Guest route `data`: `showFooter` (landing only), `showNavActions` (landing + sign-in) — read by `GuestShellComponent` from deepest active route.
- `BrandMarkComponent` (`shared/ui/brand-mark/`) — truck icon + BHCOM title; optional portal suffix. Sidebar and guest topbar.
- Profile icon opens **account menu** (`topbar.account.*`): Profile/Settings close menu only; **Log out** calls `AuthService.logout()` then navigates to `/` (landing).

## SidebarService (`portal/shell/sidebar.service.ts`)

| API | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `collapsed` / `toggle()` / `setCollapsed()` | Desktop narrow sidebar (persisted `localStorage`) |
| `mobileOpen` / `openMobile()` / `closeMobile()` | Mobile drawer (not persisted) |

On `openMobile()`: `document.body` overflow hidden. On `NavigationEnd`: `closeMobile()`.

## Mobile drawer (≤768px)

- Topbar: `LucideMenu` → `openMobile()`.
- Sidebar: `position: fixed`, slides in; brand row shows **X** (`closeMobile`), not panel collapse toggle.
- `portal-shell`: backdrop button when `mobileOpen()`; single-column grid.
- i18n: `topbar.openMenu`, `sidebar.close`, `sidebar.collapse` / `sidebar.expand`.

## Desktop sidebar

- Viewport height (`100vh`), nav area scrolls (`overflow-y` on `.sidebar__nav`).
- Brand row: `PanelLeftClose` / `PanelLeftOpen` for collapse.

## Styling

- Use `@use 'styles/breakpoints' as *` + `@include below-md` in layout SCSS.
- Content padding: CSS vars from `styles.scss` (`--layout-padding-x-mobile`, etc.).
- **Portal accent:** `PortalShellComponent` host class `portal-employee` | `portal-admin` (from `PORTAL_CONFIG`); tokens in `src/styles/_portal-accent.scss`. Login uses `.login--employee` / `.login--admin` on the same tokens. Active sidebar link: inset 3px border + tinted background; brand portal suffix uses muted accent.
